      <title>特斯拉财报值得关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-29/what-to-watch-from-tesla-earnings-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在电动汽车制造商特斯拉即将公布第四季度收益之际，Nia Impact Capital 创始人兼首席投资官 Kristin Hull 分析了特斯拉的盈利预期。她与 Caroline Hyde 和 Mike Shepard 一起在“彭博科技”节目中进行了讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-29/what-to-watch-from-tesla-earnings-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 20:18:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔称美联储并不急于降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-29/fed-is-not-in-hurry-to-lower-rates-powell-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，官员们并不急于降低利率，理由是经济强劲、劳动力市场稳健。他在华盛顿发表讲话之前，决策者一致投票决定将联邦基金利率维持在 4.25%-4.5% 的区间内。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-29/fed-is-not-in-hurry-to-lower-rates-powell-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 20:04:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纳瓦霍部落同意允许铀运输，结束六个月的僵局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/uranium-standoff-ends-as-navajo-tribe-agrees-to-allow-shipments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在经过六个月的僵局导致该公司亚利桑那州矿场的生产暂停之后，Energy Fuels Inc. 与纳瓦霍族达成协议，恢复在纳瓦霍族领土上运输铀矿石。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/uranium-standoff-ends-as-navajo-tribe-agrees-to-allow-shipments</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 20:02:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储主席鲍威尔称他没有与特朗普联系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-29/fed-s-powell-says-he-s-had-no-contact-with-trump-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔在被问及唐纳德·特朗普总统是否就利率未来问题联系过他时作出了回应。在联邦公开市场委员会决定将联邦基金利率维持在 4.25%-4.5% 区间后，他在华盛顿举行的新闻发布会上发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-29/fed-s-powell-says-he-s-had-no-contact-with-trump-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 20:01:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>DeepSeek 的模型需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-29/deepseek-s-model-demand-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Cerebras 首席执行官 Andrew Feldman 表示，每家 AI 公司对 DeepSeek 高效的开源模型都有着巨大的需求。他与 Caroline Hyde 和 Mike Shepard 一起在《彭博科技》节目中进行了讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-29/deepseek-s-model-demand-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 20:00:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管股价下跌，LendingClub 首席执行官仍信心十足</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-29/lendingclub-ceo-confident-despite-shares-drop-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在这家 P2P 贷款网站运营商发布的第一季度贷款发放预测低于普遍预期后，LendingClub 股价在盘前交易中下跌。LendingClub 首席执行官 Scott Sanborn 表示，尽管贷款额下跌，但他对前景感到乐观。他在“彭博：市场”节目中与 Scarlet Fu 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-29/lendingclub-ceo-confident-despite-shares-drop-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 19:56:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
